title: Tattoo- Joined-together/Cursive Bubble Letters, And another type of Cursive Lettering.
content:
Can someone PLEASE help me identify these fonts?! One of them looks like joined-together cursive bubble letters (Justice),and the other one, (Elizabeth) looks like some type of cursive lettering. Any help will be greatly appreciated!! Even if the fonts are custom one-of-a-kind lettering, can you name fonts that are similar to these two in which they look the most like? Thanks in advanced!
